author.bio: Hi, I'm Shilpi. I'm into Product Management. I like to think that I’m an enthusiastic and optimistic person who loves to read, write, dance, discuss, debate and ponder over the philosophies of life. Feel free to drop me a mail in case you wish to get in touch. Welcome to My Space!
